org.apache.poi.hssf.record

Class FtPioGrbitSubRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.SubRecord
      • org.apache.poi.hssf.record.FtPioGrbitSubRecord
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Duplicatable, GenericRecord 

    public final class FtPioGrbitSubRecord
extends SubRecord
    This structure appears as part of an Obj record that represents image display properties.(此结构显示为表示图像显示属性的Obj记录的一部分。)

    • Nested Class Summary

      • Nested classes/interfaces inherited from class org.apache.poi.hssf.record.SubRecord

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static int AUTO_LOAD_BIT
      A bit that specifies whether the OLE server for the object is called to load the object's data automatically when the parent workbook is opened.(一个位，指定打开父工作簿时是否调用对象的OLE服务器来自动加载对象的数据。)
      static int AUTO_PICT_BIT
      A bit that specifies whether the picture's aspect ratio is preserved when rendered in different views (Normal view, Page Break Preview view, Page Layout view and printing).(指定在不同视图（正常视图、断点预览视图、页面布局视图和打印）中渲染时是否保留图片的长宽比的位。)
      static int CAMERA_BIT
      A bit that specifies whether this is a camera picture.(指定这是否是相机图片的位。)
      static int CTL_BIT
      A bit that specifies whether this object is an ActiveX control.(指定此对象是否是Firefox控件的位。)
      static int DDE_BIT
      A bit that specifies whether the pictFmla field of the Obj record that contains this FtPioGrbit specifies a DDE reference.(指定包含此FtPioGrbit的Obj记录的pictFMla字段是否指定DTE引用的位。)
      static int DEFAULT_SIZE_BIT
      A bit that specifies whether this picture's size has been explicitly set.(一个位，指定此图片的大小是否已显式设置。)
      static int ICON_BIT
      A bit that specifies whether the picture is displayed as an icon.(指定图片是否显示为图标的位。)
      static short length 
      static int PRINT_CALC_BIT
      A bit that specifies whether this object is expected to be updated on print to reflect the values in the cell associated with the object.(一个位，指定是否希望在打印时更新此对象，以反映与该对象关联的单元格中的值。)
      static int PRSTM_BIT
      A bit that specifies whether the object data are stored in an embedding storage (= 0) or in the controls stream (ctls) (= 1).(指定对象数据是存储在嵌入存储（= 0）中还是控制流（ctls）（= 1）中的位。)
      static short sid

      • setFlagByBit

        public void setFlagByBit(int bitmask,
                         boolean enabled)
        Use one of the bitmasks MANUAL_ADVANCE_BIT ... CURSOR_VISIBLE_BIT(使用其中一个位屏蔽CLARAL_ADVANCE_BIT. Cursor_Visible_BIT)
        Parameters:
        bitmask - the bitmask to apply(位屏蔽-要应用的位屏蔽)
        enabled - if true, the bitmask will be or-ed, otherwise the bits set in the mask will be removed from the flags(启用-如果为真，位屏蔽将被或化，否则屏蔽中设置的位将从标志中删除)

        protected int getDataSize()
        Specified by:
        getDataSize in class SubRecord(SubRecord类中的getDataSize)
        Returns:
        the size of the data for this record (which is always 4 bytes less than the total record size). Note however, that ushort encoded after the record sid is usually but not always the data size.(此记录的数据大小（始终比总记录大小小4个字节）。不过请注意，记录sid之后编码的ushort通常是但不总是数据大小。)
